{"tid":1875411,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【第貳拾伍期牆紙】 敗壞之政","createTime":"2020-02-11T18:44:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-20T09:11:30.000Z","uid":253119,"like":23,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"c2212771083c7af7d3cbafad1a54a0d0078eb15c","tid":1875411,"uid":253119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T18:44:45.000Z","msg":"口罩要搶、紙巾要搶、米也要搶，社會惶惶不安。政府離地無為，我們終於無法再假裝正常生活，民眾如何能自救？<br />\n<br />\n一場疫症，揭露的並不只是香港政府的管治失效，還有中國極權的脆弱，及對國際組織的潛伏控制。<br />\n<br />\n在無能的管治下，香港迎來的會是崩壞嗎？<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n目錄<br />\n1. 醫護罷工：誰令香港陷險境？ <br />\n2. 當年今日：2003年沙士與2020年武漢肺炎  <br />\n3. 政府管治無能，醫護罷工有理 <br />\n4. 文明社會  <br />\n5. 近在咫尺的陸地，一門之隔的疫病  <br />\n6. 男兒當入貨  <br />\n7. 免於恐懼的自由  <br />\n8. 世衞的淪落並非一朝一夕<br />\n9. 國際對中國的仁慈，是天真<br />\n10. 李文亮病逝︰喚醒中國人爭取自由的心了嗎？  <br />\n11. 那些年，我們一起當的兵  <br />\n12. Enterainment is the enemy of progress<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n點擊連結用投稿衝擊牆紙：@wallpaperneedyou<br />\n<br />\n#25期 #25th<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Fx2Rgux.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFx2Rgux.jpg&h=224878be&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YnSE9Py.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYnSE9Py.jpg&h=91a70985&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4N2eege.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4N2eege.jpg&h=eef9fd0b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N68duPz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN68duPz.jpg&h=d58a03e9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HfNYFWf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHfNYFWf.jpg&h=c0fa2db7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xYbbguB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumb